description: South New Hampshire University students are able to choose their campus lunch with ease, all thanks to Munchiez Food Truck. What began as a class project for a Small Business Management class back in 2014, is now an amazing thriving student & faculty-run campus tradition that is adored by the whole SNHU community. You’ll find all sorts of American classics, like Burgers, Chicken Tenders, Mac & Cheese Bites, Jalapeno Poppers, and more crazy-tasty cuisine that’s sure to hit the spot. Andif you’re hoping to shed that Freshman 15, you’re in luck, because they’re also serving lots of healthy options (including Salad, Yogurt, Granola, and more) at this super cool truck. So if you happen to pass Munchies on your way to your next class, be sure to stop by and give this handy truck a try. You just may find that you need this unique uni food to survive those desperate last-minute study crams right before those scary final exams.
name: Munchiez Food Truck
